TITLE: Preloading Resources with ReactDOM in React Client Component (TSX)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to use ReactDOM to preload, preconnect, and prefetch DNS resources in a React client component. It imports ReactDOM from 'react-dom' and uses the preload, preconnect, and prefetchDNS methods to hint to the browser that these resources are needed. This should improve initial page load performance by loading resources early.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/05-api-reference/04-functions/generate-metadata.mdx#_snippet_68

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
'use client'

import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'

