TITLE: Using Memoized Data for Both Metadata and Page Rendering (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use a memoized data fetch function for both metadata generation and page rendering in TypeScript, ensuring the data is fetched only once.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/01-getting-started/10-metadata-and-og-images.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_7

