TITLE: Forwarding Refs in Functional Components with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use React.forwardRef to pass a ref to a functional component. It involves wrapping the component to enable proper handling of href and onClick attributes. This setup is for TypeScript in a Next.js app, depending on 'react' and 'next/link'.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/05-api-reference/02-components/link.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_25

LANGUAGE: typescript
