DESCRIPTION: Handles processing of middleware-specific headers and request validation
SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/turbopack/crates/turbopack-ecmascript/tests/tree-shaker/analyzer/next-response/output.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
