TITLE: Generating Dynamic Metadata with TypeScript - Next.js
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript snippet illustrates the usage of the `generateMetadata` function to fetch and return dynamic metadata based on route parameters. It showcases how to extend metadata with additional images when appropriate.
