TITLE: Console Enhancement Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Implements console output enhancement by wrapping standard console methods. Adds stack traces and formatting markers for improved debugging.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/turbopack/crates/turbopack-ecmascript/tests/tree-shaker/analyzer/failed-3/output.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const improveConsole = (name, stream, addStack)=>{
    const original = console[name];
    const stdio = process[stream];
    console[name] = (...args)=>{
        stdio.write(`TURBOPACK_OUTPUT_B\n`);
        original(...args);
        if (addStack) {
            const stack = new Error().stack?.replace(/^.+\n.+\n/, "") + "\n";
            stdio.write("TURBOPACK_OUTPUT_S\n");
            stdio.write(stack);
        }
        stdio.write("TURBOPACK_OUTPUT_E\n");
    };
};
```

