TITLE: Custom Random Generator
DESCRIPTION: Implements custom random string generation with specified alphabet and size.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/turbopack/crates/turbopack-ecmascript/tests/tree-shaker/analyzer/nanoid/output.md#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
let customRandom = (alphabet, size, getRandom)=>{
    let mask = (2 << (31 - Math.clz32((alphabet.length - 1) | 1))) - 1;
    let step = Math.ceil((1.6 * mask * size) / alphabet.length);
    return ()=>{
        let id = '';
        while(true){
            let bytes = getRandom(step);
            let i = step;
            while(i--){
                id += alphabet[bytes[i] & mask] || '';
                if (id.length === size) return id;
            }
        }
    };
};
```

