TITLE: Gap Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of the gap styling function that handles theme-based spacing values and responsive breakpoints
SOURCE: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/turbopack/crates/turbopack-ecmascript/tests/tree-shaker/analyzer/mui-sys/output.md#2025-04-21_snippet_36

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const gap = (props)=>{
    if (props.gap !== undefined && props.gap !== null) {
        const transformer = createUnaryUnit(props.theme, 'spacing', 8, 'gap');
        const styleFromPropValue = (propValue)=>({
                gap: getValue(transformer, propValue)
            });
        return handleBreakpoints(props, props.gap, styleFromPropValue);
    }
    return null;
};
```

